Known bugs:

Everything feels so unfinished because it is. I made all the Ui in 4 hours, that's why there is no custom icon, I'm  dumb, and too lazy to work until there is 4 hours left. (Also I planned my schedule thinking I would have Friday because I'm blind so there's that too.)
